ðŸ¤” Q. Write a program to display greeting as per time.

# Code

import time
Time = time.strftime ('%H:%M:%S')
print("Current Time = ", Time)

HTime = int(time.strftime ('%H'))

if (5 <= HTime < 12):
  print("Good Morning") 

elif (12 <= HTime < 17):
  print("Good Afternoon") 

elif (17 <= HTime <=22):
  print("Good Evening") 

else:
  print("Good Night")   


- O/P.:
Current Time = 17:40:07
Good Evening
